## Layout

Tests live under `test/` mirroring `app/`:
- `test/models/`, `test/controllers/`, `test/jobs/`, `test/components/`, `test/integration/`
- Fixtures: `test/fixtures/*.yml`

## Running

```bash
bin/rails test
bin/rails test test/models/article_test.rb   # single file
```

CI runs full suite after `bin/rails db:setup`.

## Style

- Minitest (`test "description" do` or `def test_...`)
- Use fixtures; avoid hitting external APIs (Mixin, Arweave) in unit tests
- Component tests often use placeholder `test_component_renders_something_useful` — add real assertions when changing components

## Avoid

- Upgrading to minitest 6 (incompatible with current Rails test runner on Ruby 4)
- Tests that depend on production credentials or live blockchain calls
